properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 2 at 3:54AM EST until February 2 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 25 kt with occasional gusts up to
34 kt this morning, decreasing to 15 knots this afternoon. Seas
7 to 8 feet in the Gulf Stream.

* WHERE...Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 0-20 nm, Flagler
Beach to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm.

* WHEN...Through 4 PM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON
